+/*
+  Entry points for VK_KHR_acceleration_structure / VK_KHR_ray_tracing_pipeline.
+  Extension functions are not exported by the loader, so they are resolved with
+  vkGetDeviceProcAddr when the device is created. Only valid when the owning
+  context's SupportsRayTracing() returns true.
